measurements.description: Fifty-three slightly cupped flowers and three buds on three up to 88-cm pendent inflorescences; sepals and petals yellow overlaid and speckled dark rose coalescing into stripes, yellow picotee; lip yellow overlaid maroon spots; column yellow brushed dark rose apically, maroon spots basally and underside, anther cap white; substance firm; texture matte.
